 "contentEncoded": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/crudbud/4476743656/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4057/4476743656_d89d52045f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\"></a></p>\n<p>Good morning, Nashville. Because we just love you guys so much here at Nashvillest, we&#x2019;re going to continue our annual tradition of being the one place on the internet that isn&#x2019;t foolin&#x2019; around on this fine first day of April (<a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2010/04/no-april-fools-joke-80-degree-weather-today/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">and it is </a><em><a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2010/04/no-april-fools-joke-80-degree-weather-today/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">fine</a></em><a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2010/04/no-april-fools-joke-80-degree-weather-today/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">, isn&#x2019;t it?</a>) (and clearly, some of our friends <a href=\"http://blogs.nashvillescene.com/pitw/2010/04/new_mixed-use_development_comi.php\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;blogs.nashvillescene.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">don&#x2019;t love you</a> <a href=\"http://blogs.nashvillescene.com/nashvillecream/2010/04/the_rolling_stones_at_the_end.php\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;blogs.nashvillescene.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">as much as we do</a>).&#xA0;At any rate, in the strangest instance of non-foolery, we have learned that Metro is finally hopping onto the social networking bandwagon and now has <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/MetroNashville\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.facebook.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">a Facebook fan page</a>. But dear City Paper, we never want to read the words <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/metro-joins-social-networking-craze\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">&#x201C;saucy spring break pictures of Mayor Karl Dean&#x201D; ever again</a>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Crickets. You guys. Crickets.</strong> The students at Ravenwood High School in Brentwood had their April Fools Day fun a day early&#x2013;<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=2010100331064\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">by letting thousands of crickets out into the hallways of the school at approximately 6am yesterday morning</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Free MBAs for vets.</strong> Lipscomb University is <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/education/23017733/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">offering free tuition, books and fees to any military veterans seeking an MBA</a> who are eligible through the Yellow Ribbon program.</li>\n<li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces.</strong> <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=12237472\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Watch out for that H1N1</a>! It isn&#x2019;t over yet &#x2026; A creeper in Cool Springs <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100331/WILLIAMSON01/100331067/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">flashed a jogger on Cool Springs Blvd. today</a> &#x2026; Economists are predicting that Nashville will <a href=\"http://wpln.org/?p=16283\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;wpln.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">bounce back from the recession</a> just fine &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=12239160\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">This makes us feel safe</a>, right?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/crudbud/4476743656/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Phillip Riggins</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"
